<TestCaseEntity>
   <description>Objective:&#xd;
Verify that a user can open the laptop category and view only the desired product - laptops.&#xd;
&#xd;
Preconditions:&#xd;
User is on DemoBlaze homepage.&#xd;
&#xd;
Steps:&#xd;
1. Open homepage&#xd;
2. Click on &quot;Laptops&quot; category&#xd;
3. Verify product page loads with only desired product.&#xd;
&#xd;
Expected Result:&#xd;
Desired product (in this case, laptops) page displays.</description>
